Infantry stands guard on a rainy day in Panama City. Associated Press; Photo, 
(Southland Edition) Bulldozer in Panama City tosses dirt on grave containing 
unidentified victims of recent fighting. Scene was at Garden of Peace Cemetery. 
Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
