</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
PITTSBURGH STEELERS (FOOTBALL TEAM); FOOTBALL CHAMPIONSHIPS; HOUSTON OILERS 
(FOOTBALL TEAM) 
</P>
