<TEXT>
<P>
BMI Grants HBO One-Month License Extension: Broadcast Music Inc. has agreed to 
grant a one-month extension of its license to Home Box Office Inc. "at a 
substantially higher fee." 
</P>
<P>
The agreement came in negotiations between representatives of HBO and BMI. BMI 
said that the issues raised in the lawsuit filed on Dec. 28 are still 
unresolved and that unless the parties could reach agreement in January, the 
litigation will continue. BMI filed suit against HBO to obtain a preliminary 
injunction to prevent it from using BMI repertoire on the Home Box Office 
channel after HBO's license expires Dec. 31. 
</P>
